Author: red_ossifrage
Text: They're a money saver right up to the point that you buy half the grocery store, because you are quite literally starving, and have zero judgment about what to buy so you just buy everything   They're a money saver up to the point where you have to continuously get new clothes, because randomly your ED has decided previous safe clothes now make you look fat  They're a money saver up to the point where you crater your academic/professional career, due to your instability and self-hatred, and end up a total failure :`)
